VERSION 1.0
-----------

* General
  - Unify error handling (exceptions from within subsystems, proper handling at
    controller level)
  - Unify logging (informational message when big things happen, debug messages
    for all events, and trace messages for individual actions; but how to apply
    this in auxiliary systems?)

* Application controller
  - Verify that devices get configurer properly on all required actions (new
    or updated configurations/media, device enters)
  - Verify the application doesn't crash when an configuration fails (e.g.
    device not reachable or smth)

* Website subsystem
  - Display offline kiosks

* Network subsystem
  - Preserve offline kiosks

* Repository subsystem
  - GetMediaRevision & GetConfigurationRevision, zo geen redundant loads @
    checkout


